    <string name="use_alarm_manager">使用AlarmManager来唤醒</string>
    <string name="use_alarm_manager_desc">In addition to the system broadcast, the AlarmManager is used to wake up. This method will synchronize the time every one minute, but it will also affect the sleep state of the mobile phone.\n** Remarks: There is power consumption, and wake up will be suspended after turning off the screen (this state saves power), so it is recommended to turn off the button or turn off the screen when not in use</string>
