    <string name="settings_clock_advanced">高级设置 Advanced</string>
    <string name="settings_clock_advanced_clock_sync">时钟对齐 Clock Synchronization</string>
    <string name="settings_clock_advanced_clock_sync_desc">如果息屏显示的时间更新不准确，您可以在这里更换时钟对齐方式。 If the clock does not update correctly on your AoD, you can change the mode of sync here.</string>
    <string name="settings_clock_alignment_info">时钟同步是做什么的？ What does Clock Synchronization do?</string>
    <string name="settings_clock_alignment_info_desc">如果您发现时间没有正确刷新，您可以尝试更换时钟对齐方式。此项设置中您有四个选项，有着不同的时间准确性和耗电量。请注意此为高级设置！如果不明白，请不要随意修改！ These settings allow you to pick from four options to change the balance between clock accuracy on the always on display and power consumption. If you notice the clock on the AoD isn\'t updating as it should do, try changing to a different synchronization setting\nPlease note this is an <b>advanced option</b>, don\'t touch it if you don\'t understand what it does</string>
    <string name="settings_clock_alignment_system_broadcast">系统广播模式 System Broadcast Mode</string>
    <string name="settings_clock_alignment_system_broadcast_desc">此设置仅依赖系统的广播来更新时间，一般挺准的，但是尤其在氢OS存在问题，耗电量最少。 This option relies on just the system broadcast of time updates. It is fairly accurate, but does have problems, especially on HydrogenOS. This uses the least amount of power.</string>
    <string name="settings_clock_alignment_alarmmanager">闹钟管理器模式 Alarm Manager Mode</string>
    <string name="settings_clock_alignment_alarmmanager_desc">此选项调用安卓闹钟管理系统作为系统广播的补充。每分钟刷新会获得更高的准确性，会增加耗电量。开启此选项时建议通过设置定时关屏或通过倒扣手机/口袋模式触发关屏。 This option uses the android Alarm Manager system in addition to the system broadcast. This allows for more accurate updates every minute, at the expense of a higher power consumption. If you use this option, it\'s recommended to use one of the options to turn the screen off after some time.</string>
    <string name="settings_clock_alignment_alarmmanager_timeout">闹钟管理器-超时模式 Alarm Manager with Timeout Mode <b>默认(Default)</b></string>
    <string name="settings_clock_alignment_alarmmanager_timeout_desc">此选项调用闹钟管理器，但使用定时任务唤醒，每分钟同步一次。是最平衡的选项。This option uses the Alarm Manager, but uses a \'fixed time task\' to wake up and synchronize once a minute. This is the most balanced of the options.</string>
    <string name="settings_clock_alignment_choreographer">编舞者模式 Choreographer Mode</string>
    <string name="settings_clock_alignment_choreographer_desc">此选项使用动态时钟唤醒，将提供非常准确的时钟对齐，会增加耗电量。当手机深度睡眠时会出现不准确的情况。开启此选项时建议通过设置定时关屏或通过倒扣手机/口袋模式触发关屏。 This option uses an animated clock to wake up, which provides a very accurate time synchronization, at the expense of power. It may also be inaccurate when the phone enters deep sleep. If you use this option, it\'s recommended to use one of the options to turn the screen off after some time.</string>


